{"tid":1040572,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[一拳超人]何為英雄","createTime":"2019-02-28T07:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T05:48:11.000Z","uid":176797,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53954ed7c7d7329cec6af0e6cd952d6b03f6d553","tid":1040572,"uid":176797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"何為英雄，簡單嚟講，就係琦玉一開始講嘅：興趣使然的英雄。<br />\n做英雄，重要嘅係興趣，或者係自身嘅選擇。<br />\n當中，主角嘅英雄形態：有興趣，有實力，價值觀正確，隨性，唔離地。<br />\n係呢個基礎上，將呢幾樣特質逐一解構，就係英雄協會各類配角。<br />\n冇實力嘅就係無證騎士，冇實力冇興趣嘅就係king，做事嚴謹唔隨性嘅就係童帝，冇熱血懶懶散散嘅就係邦古。餓狼就係冇興趣做英雄。而對應返甜心假面，就係扭曲嘅價值觀"},{"pid":"e7d9619009f921dfd51727cf81dbf907babe82a5","tid":1040572,"uid":38540,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦"},{"pid":"768b659c9244fc5f82e194c224a31a3af5218ba6","tid":1040572,"uid":17678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/115922_814c4448a0db2e83787ff106ab7a3f40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F115922_814c4448a0db2e83787ff106ab7a3f40.png&h=f9938a56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1254e3cb8bf96078170649e52479fce71bb17f0b","tid":1040572,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"又有傻仔睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02508c5fb12b2675a52b5d8baf6619d9f732fedb","tid":1040572,"uid":2785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"你講乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76643c2a84757ad1d0682e616eddca4ad0615511","tid":1040572,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:25:26.000Z","msg":"標準等案: 將連登高登一齊屌就係英雄"},{"pid":"4089353b46b02e8e2f8a9334793995de5d395f9a","tid":1040572,"uid":3293